4 0 0 50 0 0 10 0.0000 4 150 3375 8550 3420 The output summer  is clears at the start of each communation cycle.\001
4 0 0 50 0 0 10 0.0000 4 150 3105 8550 3660 during the commutation cycle, it accumulates the calue of each\001
4 0 0 50 0 0 10 0.0000 4 135 915 8550 3900 selected FIR filter.\001
